bnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsGyHxVR.png&h=586ef74f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/KDEWCoh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKDEWCoh.jpg&h=8e03693f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">參考網站(USUM資訊)</span></strong></ins>：<br />\n培育入門<span style=\"color: red;\">(新手必睇)</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://tut1.hkgpkm.pw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftut1.hkgpkm.pw&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt30trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=0af06c4e\" target=\"_blank\">http://tut1.hkgpkm.pw</a><br />\n<br />\n傷害計算<br />\n<a href=\"https://pokemon-trainer.net/sm/dmcs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpokemon-trainer.net%2Fsm%2Fdmcs%2F&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt30trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=754220e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://pokemon-trainer.net/sm/dmcs/</a> (日)<br />\n<a href=\"https://pokemonshowdown.com/damagecalc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpokemonshowdown.com%2Fdamagecalc%2F&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt30trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=9a09ec09\" target=\"_blank\">https://pokemonshowdown.com/damagecalc/</a> (英)<br />\n<br />\n個體計算<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.serebii.net/games/iv-calcsm.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.serebii.net%2Fgames%2Fiv-calcsm.shtml&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt30trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=d33c5565\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.serebii.net/games/iv-calcsm.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\n最大耐久指數計算<br />\n<a href=\"http://pkc.client.jp/w/defmax.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpkc.client.jp%2Fw%2Fdefmax.html&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt30trSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=92030d46\" target=\"_blank\">http://pkc.client.jp/w/defmax.html</a> (日)<br />\n<br />\n圖鑑/資料網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://serebii.net/pokedex-sm/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fserebii.net%2Fpokedex-sm%2F&d=EOIuueFNblo0QISdjyyt30trSv